<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>ArgumentException on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/argumentexception/</link><description>Recent content in ArgumentException on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/argumentexception/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] PowerShell ArgumentException in PowerShell</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/powershell/powershell-argument-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/powershell/powershell-argument-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="powershell-argumentexception-fix"&gt;PowerShell ArgumentException Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ArgumentExceptions occur when a method or cmdlet receives an argument that doesn&amp;rsquo;t meet its expected type, range, or format requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;.NET methods and PowerShell cmdlets validate their arguments. An ArgumentException means the value is within the correct type but outside the valid range or doesn&amp;rsquo;t meet constraints.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Numeric value out of allowed range&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;String value doesn&amp;rsquo;t match expected format (e.g., path, regex)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Null passed where a non-null value is required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enum value not in the allowed set&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collection count doesn&amp;rsquo;t match expected size&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="1-validate-argument-ranges"&gt;1. Validate argument ranges&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Check parameter constraints&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Get-Help Some-Command -Parameter ParameterName
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example: port must be 1-65535&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$port = &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;99999&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# ArgumentException&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$port = &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;8080&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Valid&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="2-check-argument-type"&gt;2. Check argument type&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Verify type matches&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$value.GetType()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Convert if needed&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$number = [&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;42&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# String to int&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$date = [&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DateTime&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;2024-01-01&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# String to DateTime&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="3-handle-null-values"&gt;3. Handle null values&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: null argument&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$nullValue = $null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;System.IO.File&lt;/span&gt;]::ReadAllText($nullValue)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# RIGHT: validate first&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; ($null &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-ne&lt;/span&gt; $path &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-and&lt;/span&gt; (Test-Path $path)) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;System.IO.File&lt;/span&gt;]::ReadAllText($path)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="4-use-valid-enum-values"&gt;4. Use valid enum values&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Check allowed values&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;enum&lt;/span&gt;]::GetValues([&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;System.ConsoleColor&lt;/span&gt;])
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Use valid value&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Console&lt;/span&gt;]::ForegroundColor = [&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ConsoleColor&lt;/span&gt;]::Red &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Valid&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="powershell-type-error"&gt;Type Mismatch&lt;/a&gt; — type conversion errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="powershell-parameter-binding"&gt;ParameterBindingException&lt;/a&gt; — parameter issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="invalid-operation"&gt;InvalidOperation&lt;/a&gt; — operation errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>ArgumentException</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/argument-exception/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/argument-exception/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;ArgumentException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when a method is called with an argument that doesn&amp;rsquo;t meet its requirements. This can happen when the argument is null, out of range, or of the wrong type.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passing null where non-null is required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Argument outside valid range&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wrong type of argument&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invalid string format&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Not validating input
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; processName &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; printfn &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, %s!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;ToUpper()&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ArgumentException if null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Validate input
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; processName &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; System.String.IsNullOrEmpty&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; failwith &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Name cannot be null or empty&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; printfn &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello, %s!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;ToUpper()&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: No bounds checking
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; getElement idx &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;a array&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[&lt;/span&gt;idx&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ArgumentOutOfRangeException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Check bounds
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; getElement idx &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;a array&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; idx &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; 0 &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; idx &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Length &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; failwithf &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Index %d out of range 0..%d&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; idx &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Length &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; 1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[&lt;/span&gt;idx&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Null argument
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;s&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;ToUpper() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ArgumentNullException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Invalid enum value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; color &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;enum&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;System.ConsoleColor&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; 999 &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ArgumentOutOfRangeException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Negative count
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Array.zeroCreate&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;int&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;1 &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ArgumentOutOfRangeException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/index-out-of-range"&gt;IndexOutOfRangeException&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/invalid-operation5"&gt;InvalidOperationException&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>ArgumentException in F#</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-argumentexception/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-argumentexception/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;ArgumentException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when a function receives an argument that is invalid in value but valid in type. This includes &lt;code&gt;ArgumentNullException&lt;/code&gt; for null values.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Null passed to non-null parameter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invalid argument value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wrong argument combination&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Out of range values&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Validate arguments:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; setAge &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;age&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; int&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; age &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; 0 &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; age &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; 150 &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; invalidArg &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;age&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;sprintf &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Invalid age: %d&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; age&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; age
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Use option types:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; connect &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;host&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; option&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;port&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; int option&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
